This program should display the letter C in rainbow colors for ~2 seconds.
Then the display should go blank for ~1 second.
The letter O will be displayed in rainbow colors for ~2 seconds.
The display will go blank for ~1 second.
A green shamrock will appear on the display for ~2 seconds.
The display will go blank.

Compile this program using:
cc -o crissao crissao.c -L ~/lib -I ~/include -lsense
